{"id": 59529, "date": "2025-09-01T04:00:50", "date_gmt": "2025-09-01T11:00:50", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59529"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T10:29:32", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-24T17:29:32", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-1-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/01/kingdom-of-days-september-1-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 1"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1969:\u00a0</strong>Child plays a Labor Day gig at Freak Beach in East Long Branch, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4127\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1969-0901/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1969-0901.jpg?fit=610%2C573&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"610,573\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1969-0901\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1969-0901.jpg?fit=610%2C573&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4127 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1969-0901.jpg?resize=610%2C573&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"610\" height=\"573\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1969-0901.jpg?w=610&amp;ssl=1 610w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1969-0901.jpg?resize=300%2C282&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 610px) 100vw, 610px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band headlines an outdoor show at Garfield Park in Long Branch. The set list features the only known live recording of &#8220;It&#8217;s Time to Go Home,&#8221; covers of &#8220;Little Queenie,&#8221; &#8220;(Get Your Kicks On) Route 66&#8221; and &#8220;The Night They Drove Old Dixie Down,&#8221; the fun &#8220;Dance Dance Dance&#8221; and more.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I1hdt69lcSw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SsY7TiOjVfM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20844\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-09-01/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?fit=1515%2C1640&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1515,1640\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598198950&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-09-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?fit=758%2C820&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20844 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?resize=758%2C821&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"821\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?w=1515&amp;ssl=1 1515w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?resize=277%2C300&amp;ssl=1 277w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?resize=946%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 946w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?resize=768%2C831&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-09-01.jpg?resize=1419%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1419w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play two shows at Fat City in Seaside Heights, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Recording sessions for\u00a0<em>Darkness on the Edge of Town</em> continue at The Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Darkness descends on the Masonic Temple Theater in Detroit, where Bruce and the band debut their cover of &#8220;Chimes of Freedom&#8221; and play the last known &#8220;Lost in the Flood&#8221; for 22 years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_VGPkBaF0X0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"__vd_iu19oi_share-permalink\">\n<div class=\"__vd_iu19oi_pre-wrap\">\n<div class=\"__vd_iu19oi_pre\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://videopress.com/embed/6l3WlkHI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"__vd_iu19oi_pre-wrap\"></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eOg51wxjbWo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:</strong> Bruce takes in the Jacksons&#8217; Victory Tour at JFK Stadium in Philadelphia. Had he let the tour organizers know a bit earlier in the day, the audience might have been treated to a Springsteen guest appearance.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29081\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-09-01-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?fit=881%2C1244&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"881,1244\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598296085&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-09-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?fit=725%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29081 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?resize=758%2C1070&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1070\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?w=881&amp;ssl=1 881w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?resize=725%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 725w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1984-09-01.jpg?resize=768%2C1084&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p>Also today,\u00a0<em>American Top 40\u00a0</em>host Casey Kasem introduces Bruce&#8217;s latest hit single &#8220;Cover Me&#8221; with the story behind Springsteen&#8217;s new and improved physique.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-59529-10\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-01-AT40.mp3?_=10\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-01-AT40.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-01-AT40.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce wraps up a six-show Giants Stadium stand on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour with the final &#8220;Jersey Girl&#8221; of the tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Emg8kiqwMmg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-vQFwNj9F-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/vQFwNj9F?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20847\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-09-01/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?fit=2429%2C1025&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2429,1025\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598199326&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?fit=758%2C320&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20847 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?resize=758%2C320&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?w=2429&amp;ssl=1 2429w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?resize=300%2C127&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?resize=1024%2C432&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?resize=768%2C324&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?resize=1536%2C648&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?resize=2048%2C864&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-01.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band hold their last rehearsal before the kick-off of the Amnesty International &#8211; Human Rights Now Tourat Wembley Stadium in London. Of particular note: the band starts their warm-up by covering Sting&#8217;s &#8220;King of Pain,&#8221; which Bruce has never performed live.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-59529-11\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Amnesty-Rehearsal.mp3?_=11\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Amnesty-Rehearsal.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Amnesty-Rehearsal.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the reunited E Street Band play their second of three shows at the MCI Center in Washington, DC.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-59529-12\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Track_01__Merged.mp3?_=12\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Track_01__Merged.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Track_01__Merged.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>2001:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Clarence Clemons and the Temple of Soul on stage at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park. Their performance of &#8220;Raise Your Hand&#8221; will be released three years later on Clarence&#8217;s <em>Live in Asbury Park Vol. II</em> album.</p>\n<div id=\"v-fH8ltr8g-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/fH8ltr8g?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3NHIzOVOswc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2011:\u00a0</strong>In town to drop Evan off at Boston College, Bruce encounters a street musician named David Gonzalez plying his craft in Boston Public Garden. Bruce and David chat, and David lets Bruce try his guitar. For lunch, Bruce has a tuna sandwich at the Deluxe Station Diner, and later that evening, Bruce catches up with old friend Peter Wolf over dinner at Via Matta. The two then catch the Roy Sludge Trio&#8217;s show in Cambridge.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CwmHLXh-Gow?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20849\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2011-09-01a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?fit=1310%2C1642&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1310,1642\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598199896&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2011-09-01a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?fit=758%2C950&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20849 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?resize=758%2C950&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"950\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?w=1310&amp;ssl=1 1310w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?resize=239%2C300&amp;ssl=1 239w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?resize=817%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 817w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?resize=768%2C963&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01a.jpg?resize=1225%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1225w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20850\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2011-09-01b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?fit=1031%2C1235&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1031,1235\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598199937&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2011-09-01b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?fit=758%2C908&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20850 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?resize=758%2C908&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"908\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?w=1031&amp;ssl=1 1031w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?resize=250%2C300&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?resize=855%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 855w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2011-09-01b.jpg?resize=768%2C920&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>Bruce sends a message at Washington DC&#8217;s Nationals Park: that last show in East Rutherford was no one-off. The River Tour is now the Autobiography Tour, as Bruce turns in another mostly-chronological set, once again opening with a string-laden &#8220;New York City Serenade&#8221;\u00a0 and featuring generous helpings of pre-<em>Born to Run</em> material. &#8220;Better Days&#8221; makes its tour debut representing the 1992-1993 years, and &#8220;Secret Garden&#8221; makes another appearance in the encores. In attendance tonight: Olympic gold medalist Katie Ledecky.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/V--C10U3kqQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7cZE-g6im3U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups a